                    <div class="my-personality-title heading small-frc">My Personality</div>
                    <div class="my-personality-desc desc">
                        I am a passionate human. Perhaps a little anxious but I can work my way out and adapt to any work dynamic. I am never afraid of asking the right questions or being an overt critique. I am also a compassionate person who is always willing to learn from others or to spread my knowledge. I make some innocuous mistakes but sometimes you poke around and you find out and I genuinely believe that's what helps you grow as person without limiting yourself.
                    </div>
                    <div class="read-more-div">
                        <a class="read-more" href="/blog">Get even more personal with my blog <img src="/assets/img/icons/blog/return_key_arrow.png"
