                    </div>
                    <div class="my-passion-title heading small-frc">My Passion</div>
                    <div class="my-passion-desc desc">
                        Whenever I encounter a complex problem, I want to dissect it to the atomic level and learn the fundamentals. It can be a software one, economic one or a mechanical one. Maybe that's the reason I'm more into DIYs. Also, I am optimistic and enthusiastic about future. So, I am learning as much as I can to survive and indulge tomorrow. I am never hesitant to learn anything new about Space, AI, Extended realities etc.
                    </div>
